<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <style>
      * {
        box-sizing: border-box;
      }

      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
      }

      .container {
        margin: 0 auto;
        max-width: 600px;
        padding: 20px;
        background-color: #f9f9f9;
        border-radius: 10px;
        box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
      }

      .delv-head {
        font-size: 24px;
        line-height: 1.2;
        text-transform: none;
        font-weight: 800;
        margin-bottom: 25px;
      }

      .delv-speach {
        font-size: 18px;
        line-height: 1.4;
        text-transform: none;
        font-weight: 400;
      }

      .delv-close {
        font-size: 16px;
        line-height: 1.6;
        text-transform: none;
        font-weight: 500;
      }

      .delv-comp {
        font-size: 16px;
        line-height: 1.6;
        text-transform: none;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <img
        src="{{ logo_main }}"
        height="42"
        width="112"
      />
      <p class="delv-head">One last thing,</p>

      <p class="delv-speach">
        We hope your renovation project was a resounding success and brought your vision to life. 
        We would like to take this opportunity to thank you for choosing {{ company_name }} to make it happen.
      </p>

      <p class="delv-speach">
        Your trust and cooperation made the journey smooth and rewarding. We hope you are enjoying the fruits of our labor as much as we enjoyed bringing it to fruition.
      </p>

      <p class="delv-speach">
        It was a pleasure working with you, and we look forward to assisting you with any future projects you may have. We're always here to turn your construction dreams into reality.
      </p>

      <p class="delv-speach">
        Thank you again for your trust and support. We look forward to the prospect of working together again in the future.ðŸ˜Š
      </p>

      <p class="delv-close">Best regards,</p>
      <p class="delv-close">{{ company_name }}</p>
      <p class="delv-comp">{{ office_phone }}</p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
